A few points. "63 - Graph Theory" is the same as "184 - Modern Graph Theory. It's fine since 184 is an updated edition of 63 anyway.

121 is supposed to be a revised edition of both 59 and 69 together in one book (Cyclotomic fields I and II) but instead is a copy of 59
